## 🎯 MCP Priority Guide

| MCP | Optimal For | Trigger Keywords | Priority |
|-----|-------------|------------------|----------|
| **claude-mem** | Reusing past solutions | "did we", "how did we", "remember" | 1 |
| **git-flow-master** | Versioned commits | "commit", "release", "update", "patch" | 2 |
| **chrome-devtools** | UI debugging/testing | "debug UI", "test page", "screenshot" | 3 |
| **web-reader** | Reading documentation | "read URL", "fetch page", "docs" | 4 |
| **web-search-prime** | Latest info | "latest docs", "current info" | 4 |

